name: Speedbreaker (cheyenne.deloach)
description:
Speedbreaker is a short arcade game with a mix of mechanics from Arkanoid, pinball, and Pac-Man. You will quickly move through 30 levels that each take less than 5 seconds to beat (and you are on the clock!).

This game was built in Unreal Engine 5.0

All assets were made by me, except for 2 fonts from https://www.dafont.com/

Estrogen Font by Apostrophic Labs

Unscreen MK Font by Manfred Klein
